  "commit_message": "fix: parse Ethereal response props without polynomial regex backtracking\n\ngetTestMessageUrl() extracted the trailing bracket group of the server\nresponse with a regex that CodeQL flagged for polynomial backtracking on\nadversarial responses (js/polynomial-redos). Replace it with linear string\nscanning; a 200k-case fuzz comparison confirmed the old and new parsers\nextract identical values.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
